'''Iotran Braceman Armor''' was a type of heavy [[Armor/Legends|armor]] suit that was utilized by the [[Braceman|Bracemen]], who were veteran police officers of [[Iotra]], a [[Planet/Legends|world]] on the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. During the [[Standard year/Legends|years]] of the [[Jedi Civil War]], many [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]] favored this kind of armor.

